            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1627992540395-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>tofu yakitori skewers</strong> with the <strong>candied sweet potato </strong>and<strong> quick-pickled cucumber</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>Japanese-style mayo</strong> over the sweet potatoes and garnish with the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
